{"type": "article", "id": 15172, "title": "“flow”椅子", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-21T07:39:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 44, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115213RNSzDVMFXiP2o3Gr.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t擅长极简风格的日本设计师安积朋子为英国家具品牌 ercol 设计了一把椅子“flow”，正在伦敦设计节（london design festival）上展出。采用榉木材质，通过蒸汽弯曲技术，将椅子的外形做的非常优雅，适合想要营造古典气氛的现代家庭。此外，它可以堆叠起来，利于节省空间。有黑、白、天然榉木三种颜色。<a href=\"http://www.ercol.com/ranges/flow/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142439PMI9cK7udrOE8WC0.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142440adZR4rzp1cgtFIJL.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"613\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142441Y6EuFGZh9mTson10.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"682\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.83374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}